{"article_id":"ZtvjDxArx1u62bn8","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"But even as he accepted that reality ,","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"he appeared determined to deliver a tough critique of Mr. Obama ' s economic policies in the face of an unreceptive crowd .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"He suggested","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"that their support for Mr. Obama was misplaced ,","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"and that his policies as president would make their lives better .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"\" If I did not believe","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"that my policies and my leadership would help families of color","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"- and families of any color -","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"more than the policies and leadership of President Obama ,","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"I would not be running for president , \"","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Later , in an interview with Neil Cavuto on Fox News , Mr. Romney said","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"that the booing was not a surprise .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"\" We expected that , of course , \"","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"Mr. Romney said .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"\" But ,","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"you know ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"I am going to give the same message to the N.A.A.C.P .","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"that I give across the country ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"which is that Obamacare is killing jobs . \"","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Although Mr. Obama , the country ' s first African-American president , won 95 percent of the black vote in 2008","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"according to exit polls ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"Mr. Romney is not ceding any ground","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"in what is expected to be a close election in November .","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"The black vote ,","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"which is still overwhelmingly in Mr. Obama ' s column ,","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"could prove crucial in swing states like North Carolina and Virginia .","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"In May , Mr. Romney hired a consultant , Tara Wall ,","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"to help with outreach efforts to black voters ,","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"and he also visited a charter school in West Philadelphia ,","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"where he was heckled .","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"But his appearance at the N.A.A.C.P . was his most direct wooing of black voters this campaign .","depth":4},{"id":32,"text":"Mr. Romney pointed to economic sufferings of the group ,","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"as he has","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"when speaking to Hispanic voters , another critical voting bloc","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"that he may have trouble winning over .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"\" The unemployment rate , the duration of unemployment , average income , median family wealth are all worse in the black community , \"","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"Newsletter Sign Up","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"Continue reading the main story","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"Please verify","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"you 're not a robot","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"by clicking the box .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Invalid email address .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Please re-enter .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"You must select a newsletter","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"to subscribe to .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"Sign Up","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"You will receive emails","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"containing news content , updates and promotions from The New York Times .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"You may opt-out at any time .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"You agree to receive occasional updates and special offers for The New York Times 's products and services .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Thank you for subscribing .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"An error has occurred .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"Please try again later .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"View all New York Times newsletters .","depth":3},{"id":56,"text":"Many in the audience gave Mr. Romney credit","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"for speaking to the group ,","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"but said","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"they were frustrated with certain aspects of his speech .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"\" I give him thumbs up","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"for being courageous , \"","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"said William Braxton , 59 , a retiree from Charles County , Md .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"But Mr. Braxton said","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"he took issue with Mr. Romney ' s assertion","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"that he would be a better president for blacks .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"\" I was shocked , \"","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"Mr. Braxton said .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"\" Never , ever have I heard him say anything","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"about how he would help the poor or underprivileged , let alone the black community .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Maybe his view is that he could tell us what we want to hear ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"and we ' re supposed to swallow it . \"","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"Donna Payne , 48 , of Washington ,","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"who was at the convention as a representative of the Human Rights Campaign , a gay rights group ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"Mr. Romney \" did the best","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"he could , \"","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"before dissolving in laughter .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"\" To say he would repeal Obama ' s health care plan is absolutely a joke , \"","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Ms. Payne said .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"\" I can ' t believe","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"he had the nerve","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"to even bring up repealing the plan in the middle","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"of speaking to an audience","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"that fought hard for the health care plan and for coverage .","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"It ' s a total misread of who you ' re talking to . \"","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"In recent national polls , Mr. Obama overwhelmingly leads Mr. Romney among black voters ,","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"many of whom are suspicious of Mr. Romney ' s record on civil rights and diversity ,","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"especially when he was the governor of Massachusetts .","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"Upon taking office , for instance ,","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"he eliminated the state ' s Office of Affirmative Action .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"Mr. Romney is also a member of the Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints ,","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"which until 1978 barred blacks from entering the priesthood .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"But Mr. Romney ' s father , George W. Romney , a former governor of Michigan , was known for his strong support of civil rights .","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"Mr. Romney mentioned his father near the end of his speech ,","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"saying ,","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"\" He was a man of the fairest instincts , and a man of faith","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"who knew","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"that every person was a child of God . \"","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"Mr. Obama was invited to address the group as well ;","depth":5},{"id":100,"text":"he cited a scheduling conflict .","depth":5},{"id":101,"text":"Vice President Joseph R. Biden Jr. will speak at the convention on Thursday .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":203,"left":139,"right":202,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":128,"right":138,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":121,"right":127,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":112,"right":120,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":112,"left":103,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"}